'''丽贝卡·D·科斯塔'''（{{lang-en|Rebecca Dazai Costa}}，{{bd|1955年|4月11日|}}）是一位[[美国|美国]][[社會生物學|社會生物學]]家<ref name="Tavis Smiley Rebecca Costa">{{cite interview|url=https://www.pbs.org/wnet/tavissmiley/interviews/sociobiologist-rebecca-costa/|title=Sociobiologist Rebecca Costa|first=Rebecca|last=Costa|interviewer=[[Tavis_Smiley|Tavis Smiley]]|work=[[Public_Broadcasting_Service|PBS]]|date=12 November 2010|accessdate=15 April 2012|subject-link=Rebecca D. Costa|archive-date=2018-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180112160213/https://www.pbs.org/wnet/tavissmiley/interviews/sociobiologist-rebecca-costa/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[未来学家|未来学家]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Can Entrepreneurs, Stuck On An Island for a Few Days, Solve the World's Biggest Problems?|work=[[Time_(magazine)|TIME]]|url=http://moneyland.time.com/2011/10/04/can-a-bunch-of-entrepreneurs-stuck-on-an-island-for-a-few-days-solve-the-worlds-biggest-problems/|first=Dan|last=Kadlec|date=4 October 2011|accessdate=15 April 2012|archive-date=2012-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009022735/http://moneyland.time.com/2011/10/04/can-a-bunch-of-entrepreneurs-stuck-on-an-island-for-a-few-days-solve-the-worlds-biggest-problems/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Rebecca Costa biography|work=Rebecca D. Costa|url=http://www.rebeccacosta.com/about-rebecca.htm|date=9 January 2018|accessdate=9 January 2018|archive-date=2018-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181010005639/http://www.rebeccacosta.com/about-rebecca.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[科普|科普]]作家<ref name="Watchman's Rattle Amazon">{{cite book|title=The Watchman's Rattle: Thinking Our Way Out of Extinction: Rebecca Costa|isbn=1593156057}}</ref>，主要作品有《守夜人的钟声：我们时代的危机和出路》（''The Watchman's Rattle: Thinking Our Way Out of Extinction''）等。

